{"tid":286574,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"迴旋處如何正確行駛","createTime":"2017-06-16T16:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-17T11:54:36.000Z","uid":116996,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f2f76ab93094e3cd994360a6f40ed2fc66a9c362","tid":286574,"uid":116996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"留意12秒左上白車。<br />\n<br />\n因為都吾知誰是誰非，希望有經驗巴打解答。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/rE5-pQITatc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FrE5-pQITatc&d=PDO%2FvFXHw%2B%2BijV430fdr%2BgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=95b17313\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/rE5-pQITatc</a><br />\n<br />\n利申:新手出post"},{"pid":"e768004b04c5c934082b5908f7e1d53361ca69f7","tid":286574,"uid":7644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:54:51.000Z","msg":"早啲cut去左線出就最安全"},{"pid":"4c2313f6c47b0ff1b52e97d527653c8a7d00cf26","tid":286574,"uid":84808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:55:01.000Z","msg":"一定係大路車岩"},{"pid":"6b4819e1d7f79cd614501309525345f0093ee9a0","tid":286574,"uid":7644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早啲cut去左線出就最安全</blockquote><br />\n最好打埋燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb617511629525e603c149bde97ff12dfd664d88","tid":286574,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"白車有咩錯"},{"pid":"c08a0e97a419ff0f49d6271ebb5c6d0a0114978f","tid":286574,"uid":84808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"如果左右線都有車而右線車想出路口係右線車岩"},{"pid":"01b0d7b587d42155bd4dc7bd96bf2d43c6088f74","tid":286574,"uid":84808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:57:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果左右線都有車而右線車想出路口係右線車岩</blockquote><br />\n利申 9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caf81085b92a594411498e55f8e88b12fbb6ab32","tid":286574,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"吾你老母咩"},{"pid":"c344997dacd67be49377c8d30f715cb0fbc78a88","tid":286574,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"2個都老不。<br />\n黑車過左咁多讓線先cut。"},{"pid":"0b6090dda046d760fa2206986cb1e5d6592ffaf4","tid":286574,"uid":73369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T16:58:50.000Z","msg":"要一早打燈過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99855d530927db2d5b71812cfc328d85e7900e7d","tid":286574,"uid":108862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:01:37.000Z","msg":"白車咁樣隊出嚟想害死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果白車要出就只適宜左轉"},{"pid":"0845975751848987eb7767d71800f4e5cc8b7eaa","tid":286574,"uid":41198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:02:18.000Z","msg":"係過左臨出前一個出口，應該要打燈攞返外線出"},{"pid":"288db846ddeb03670643709b3712836a0ddc690d","tid":286574,"uid":3355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"你出路口就要靠左線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be04a4c588eea17ec5cde4bf30004bc2daeb1636","tid":286574,"uid":22402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:12:33.000Z","msg":"淨係知吾你老母咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a43d30d744d84025554e3dd5afc222e25f15a7","tid":286574,"uid":36829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:21:29.000Z","msg":"一早打定左燈，預早d岀返外圈最穩陣，如果有打燈白色車睇到應該唔會岀"},{"pid":"c269558c6d5de27a02dc79deca41af627c7b7bce","tid":286574,"uid":90060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:24:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=potRKDghzGA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpotRKDghzGA&d=PDO%2FvFXHw%2B%2BijV430fdr%2BgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=32518597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=potRKDghzGA</a>"},{"pid":"e18b9f40286ba407453465279ccfa2f620dbaf0d","tid":286574,"uid":108862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:28:19.000Z","msg":"入迴旋處唔係下個窿就走的話 真係唔好行左線 保障自己"},{"pid":"8622410a8924c81508e689c33f18a739391cdbd1","tid":286574,"uid":31482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"呢個位好似成日都撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係新式迴旋處"},{"pid":"9f69c12044450c67c58a3ddb8c0d2ae3717adc2f","tid":286574,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:44:08.000Z","msg":"片主正線 白色車cut 線"},{"pid":"1f86dba6409028d10e8d5209d64dbcc61a045339","tid":286574,"uid":114097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:50:58.000Z","msg":"口口空白鍵係咪真係咁難打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39199a316d0b35931aa5e184a126dc43c22b4fd2","tid":286574,"uid":84993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"依個新式迴旋處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n左線入內線應該 要打右燈 或者直情右線出<br />\n白色車故之然錯 但師兄想保障自己 老乜都外圈出路口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依師兄咁內線出路口都要打左燈<br />\n好似好多都唔理新舊式 亂9咁黎出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申： 得幾年牌 有錯請指教"},{"pid":"a501e165d897da2ba1ac98cfc66845195f12dcf2","tid":286574,"uid":84993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T18:08:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白車有咩錯</blockquote><br />\n新式迴避處<br />\n左線出default 係第一個路口出<br />\n右線出就係其他路口出 如果左線出但唔係第一個路口出<br />\n就要cut 線 <br />\n白色車衰唔打燈 有車仲硬cut"},{"pid":"ab16b7cedb1d4b478c0612b9d24579cf07c4135c","tid":286574,"uid":79877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T19:18:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>白車有咩錯</blockquote><br />\n新式迴避處<br />\n左線出default 係第一個路口出<br />\n右線出就係其他路口出 如果左線出但唔係第一個路口出<br />\n就要cut 線 <br />\n白色車衰唔打燈 有車仲硬cut</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白色係衰cut線無打燈<br />\n但其實黑色都係cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到court點判？<br />\n利申: P牌"},{"pid":"f473042c25aca84d2b52d2efc56adba2cfdc2ca6","tid":286574,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T00:07:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>白車有咩錯</blockquote><br />\n新式迴避處<br />\n左線出default 係第一個路口出<br />\n右線出就係其他路口出 如果左線出但唔係第一個路口出<br />\n就要cut 線 <br />\n白色車衰唔打燈 有車仲硬cut</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n白色係衰cut線無打燈<br />\n但其實黑色都係cut<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到court點判？<br />\n利申: P牌</blockquote><br />\n如果係新式<br />\n內線其實係主線 <br />\n地下有線guide 住出<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/080741_5ea33ecc5f77aceb462f842e4bce67bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F080741_5ea33ecc5f77aceb462f842e4bce67bd.jpg&h=ae4fa453&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/17/080743_72821a770658227c0463bdd49e37e96f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F17%2F080743_72821a770658227c0463bdd49e37e96f.jpg&h=4e60697c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd1ede6bb900f941ac534df7f90ff8a1eb7492d5","tid":286574,"uid":3937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T00:13:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一早打定左燈，預早d岀返外圈最穩陣，如果有打燈白色車睇到應該唔會岀</blockquote><br />\n新式內線先係主線<br />\n睇片 部車跟線出路口"}]}